Checking distrutions

the plots below confirm that most of the predictors haves similar distributions across train and test

train$type <- "train"

test$type <- "test"

all <- rbind(train, test)

for (i in names(all)) {
x <- ggplot(data = all,aes_string(i,color="type")) + geom_density()
print(x)
}
